{"tid":211302,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[2019區議會]有冇巴絲會去選 ?","createTime":"2017-04-21T14:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T04:12:57.000Z","uid":61197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"588c967b1096a7e818572e7817cb93e6e1c32bca","tid":211302,"uid":61197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T14:07:42.000Z","msg":"見舊登之前臨近上屆區議會時都有一班巴絲幫手推人出去選  <br />\n所以想問下2019年區議會有冇巴絲有性趣想選?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果有嘅話, 早少少計劃定都差唔多架喇 <br />\n大家一齊早啲預備,踢走啲唔做嘢嘅區議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb093d7f547bd5faac5fbe4cd33333b939ada902","tid":211302,"uid":104735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T18:02:42.000Z","msg":"有意呀，但一嚟就挑戰上屆自動當選嘅選區係咪太大挑戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cbf8cb60f3d59fe541645198dd1c56d9a48d66d","tid":211302,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T01:32:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有意呀，但一嚟就挑戰上屆自動當選嘅選區係咪太大挑戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一陣你打「泛民嘅區」，佢哋就話你界票，即使佢哋長期影都唔見"},{"pid":"9a48e02acae99a8bf7c9274f896eae079bc3f4db","tid":211302,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T01:34:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有意呀，但一嚟就挑戰上屆自動當選嘅選區係咪太大挑戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自動當選唔難啦<br />\n長期高票當選既建制先難"},{"pid":"c5973720c31880d89baab69cf682d10acf5ab91d","tid":211302,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T02:55:39.000Z","msg":"有冇游b?"},{"pid":"819f4b1cc9f02adffd216d810a648f9c1e85fcd2","tid":211302,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T03:03:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有意呀，但一嚟就挑戰上屆自動當選嘅選區係咪太大挑戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自動當選唔難啦<br />\n長期高票當選既建制先難</blockquote><br />\n自動當選即係無人挑戰開，<br />\n點解唔挑戰？因為知道係死地，<br />\n例如原居民村，點都係村長食硬，<br />\n或者係有錢佬區，太多既得利益者或離地中產。"},{"pid":"ce949651e41dcb648618269c24b4b9299ad54a75","tid":211302,"uid":61197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T05:18:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有意呀，但一嚟就挑戰上屆自動當選嘅選區係咪太大挑戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想挑戰邊區 ?"},{"pid":"7e8dc48b1805e81646f6bba8f118ded9cdb5c0d7","tid":211302,"uid":61197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T09:45:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaabe32fcf81cc1f93ba5a8fb68b7114fb66a823","tid":211302,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T09:46:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有意呀，但一嚟就挑戰上屆自動當選嘅選區係咪太大挑戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自動當選唔難啦<br />\n長期高票當選既建制先難</blockquote><br />\n自動當選即係無人挑戰開，<br />\n點解唔挑戰？因為知道係死地，<br />\n例如原居民村，點都係村長食硬，<br />\n或者係有錢佬區，太多既得利益者或離地中產。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有好多自動當選既都係屋邨區<br />\n揀個d未得<br />\n我記得大埔有區有個師奶出黎選 都係差2百幾票就贏到"},{"pid":"87c197d6e40865270d69139c3a99807e50eee94e","tid":211302,"uid":25334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T10:20:34.000Z","msg":"而家好多地區組織做緊區<br />\n有興趣不如幫下佢哋手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4268214ef9cc48e28bbbf0514d8cd996e2a7f29","tid":211302,"uid":61197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T10:54:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家好多地區組織做緊區<br />\n有興趣不如幫下佢哋手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nmore details <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4efdfb49fcc3572cb278d9440b1c022d8dd36bc4","tid":211302,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T11:01:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有意呀，但一嚟就挑戰上屆自動當選嘅選區係咪太大挑戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我以前住果區條保皇自動當選幾屆<br />\n2015年比個新仔收左佢皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e16f163837e799a2e2f95b46d44d97adce8b993","tid":211302,"uid":25334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T11:26:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而家好多地區組織做緊區<br />\n有興趣不如幫下佢哋手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nmore details <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打住邊頭"},{"pid":"51a9beeb2743b1e7e729fdb90f2714640cbe2e55","tid":211302,"uid":61197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T11:45:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家好多地區組織做緊區<br />\n有興趣不如幫下佢哋手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nmore details <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打住邊頭</blockquote><br />\nKowloon West"},{"pid":"470060d189b2da2e6795b60479a9c9e1fd98f033","tid":211302,"uid":64874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T04:51:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家好多地區組織做緊區<br />\n有興趣不如幫下佢哋手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nmore details <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打住邊頭</blockquote><br />\nKowloon West</blockquote><br />\nspecific啲，油尖旺、九龍城定深水埗?<br />\n<br />\n深水埗上屆無自動當選，九龍城就土瓜灣同九龍塘附近有自動當選，紅磡就交比鄺醫生。油尖旺，想大團結就沿住彌敦道打晒旺角油麻地佐敦尖沙咀。大角咀就應該仲有人去選。"},{"pid":"eb158b61aeb77364c160857a2c82fbdb3fd0c684","tid":211302,"uid":104735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:00:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有意呀，但一嚟就挑戰上屆自動當選嘅選區係咪太大挑戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想挑戰邊區 ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n觀塘區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 九東係建制嘅地方，老人家嘅比例都好高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d168934ec1ff22a4a2c6403f4fd42c5c79962c3d","tid":211302,"uid":61197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:38:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家好多地區組織做緊區<br />\n有興趣不如幫下佢哋手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nmore details <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打住邊頭</blockquote><br />\nKowloon West</blockquote><br />\nspecific啲，油尖旺、九龍城定深水埗?<br />\n<br />\n深水埗上屆無自動當選，九龍城就土瓜灣同九龍塘附近有自動當選，紅磡就交比鄺醫生。油尖旺，想大團結就沿住彌敦道打晒旺角油麻地佐敦尖沙咀。大角咀就應該仲有人去選。</blockquote><br />\n九龍城係班建制派嘅地頭, 會唔會好難打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c08bf616ad86fd1db8a6d32ff8d677a2247cc6","tid":211302,"uid":61197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:41:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家好多地區組織做緊區<br />\n有興趣不如幫下佢哋手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nmore details <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打住邊頭</blockquote><br />\nKowloon West</blockquote><br />\nspecific啲，油尖旺、九龍城定深水埗?<br />\n<br />\n深水埗上屆無自動當選，九龍城就土瓜灣同九龍塘附近有自動當選，紅磡就交比鄺醫生。油尖旺，想大團結就沿住彌敦道打晒旺角油麻地佐敦尖沙咀。大角咀就應該仲有人去選。</blockquote><br />\n九龍城係班建制派嘅地頭, 會唔會好難打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/kc/tc_chi/members/info/dc_member_list.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtcouncils.gov.hk%2Fkc%2Ftc_chi%2Fmembers%2Finfo%2Fdc_member_list.php&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=7732faf6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/kc/tc_chi/members/info/dc_member_list.php</a>"},{"pid":"4565e67085c82e880e36d522ef2e00bc806aee59","tid":211302,"uid":64874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T17:43:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n九龍城係班建制派嘅地頭, 會唔會好難打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/kc/tc_chi/members/info/dc_member_list.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtcouncils.gov.hk%2Fkc%2Ftc_chi%2Fmembers%2Finfo%2Fdc_member_list.php&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=7732faf6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/kc/tc_chi/members/info/dc_member_list.php</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇你係為參選定為贏，以下係齋睇票數嘅豬頭骨區。<br />\n已經Assume 過四成嘅飯民會選，你可以揀呢堆區<br />\nG03 馬頭角 唐樓區，靠儲業主立案法團，現任禮義廉唔過四十，難打。<br />\nG04 樂民 15年係反地產霸權膠龐一鳴選，因為跨區選，當佢19年唔再過嚟選。<br />\nG08 太子 G09 九龍塘 有錢佬區無謂選。<br />\nG10 龍城 同馬頭角一樣。<br />\nG12 啓德北 啓晴邨 G13 啓德南 德朗邨 蝗民邨，飲鉛水仲要選保皇黨(收開著數唔轉軚)，應有此報 不過啓德區私人樓盤陸續落成，有新位可以選。<br />\nG14 海心 區議會主席，同馬頭角一樣，如果有人才瞓身做，可能創奇跡。<br />\nG15 土瓜灣北 李慧琼子老巢，想出名就同佢選<br />\nG16 土瓜灣南 15年老鴿衰咸濕兼換人選，鼠系以過六成票搶到手，而白鴿原候選人已調到愛民邨，如果有人才以素人身份做，19年可以高票落敗。<br />\nG17 鶴園海逸 15年係鼠系海逸豪園業主會主席KO禮義廉老人家，可以一試。<br />\nG17打後係紅磡同愛民邨附近，正如之前講過紅磡就去幫鄺醫生手，而愛民邨就白鴿有辦事處，無謂浪費彈藥。<br />\n<br />\n想有氣勢就G03,04,14,15,16連住選。15年林依麗團隊空降挑戰G03,14同15，最好成績有三成。如果正正經經地做，無第三者鎅票，可能可以繼續選落去。"},{"pid":"c2843cec50b65c242d7a3e7581076c2a5de7a608","tid":211302,"uid":61197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T18:20:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n九龍城係班建制派嘅地頭, 會唔會好難打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/kc/tc_chi/members/info/dc_member_list.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtcouncils.gov.hk%2Fkc%2Ftc_chi%2Fmembers%2Finfo%2Fdc_member_list.php&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=7732faf6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/kc/